1
00:01:37,930 --> 00:01:40,990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,090 --> 00:01:43,990
[Episode 7]

3
00:02:14,470 --> 00:02:15,120
It's fine.

4
00:02:15,210 --> 00:02:16,010
No one is here.

5
00:02:20,530 --> 00:02:22,270
Are you here to laugh at me?

6
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:24,870
Yes.

7
00:02:25,290 --> 00:02:26,620
I came up to laugh at you.

8
00:02:26,770 --> 00:02:27,410
Keep doing it.

9
00:02:27,410 --> 00:02:29,270
I'm not in the mood for your jokes.

10
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:33,660
You shouldn't be called Xu Miyu,

11
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,750
but Xu Eyu, which means harsh words.

12
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:37,870
Xu Miyu wasn't my real name.

13
00:02:39,310 --> 00:02:40,560
My stepsister's name

14
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,690
has the word Mi in it.

15
00:02:42,829 --> 00:02:44,290
So, my mom changed my name.

16
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:46,910
She said sisters should match.

17
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:50,160
Actually, she just wanted
to please my stepfather.

18
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:52,120
Then, I've been

19
00:02:52,370 --> 00:02:53,630
called Xu Miyu

20
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:54,750
for over 20 years,

21
00:02:55,590 --> 00:02:58,350
flattering them with sweet words
for over 20 years.

22
00:02:58,350 --> 00:03:01,150
I thought sincerity could finally
win sincerity,

23
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:02,280
but I didn't expect

24
00:03:04,710 --> 00:03:06,640
to fail miserably in the end.

25
00:03:07,010 --> 00:03:07,870
I'm like a joke.

26
00:03:10,110 --> 00:03:12,970
Have you ever heard of a bird
called Barnacle Goose?

27
00:03:15,020 --> 00:03:17,020
They live in the Arctic Circle.

28
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:19,170
To avoid predators,

29
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:21,750
they all build their nests on cliffs.

30
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:24,350
But there is no food up there.

31
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:26,840
The fledglings that haven't learned
to fly yet

32
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,590
have to risk their lives
and jump off the cliff

33
00:03:28,590 --> 00:03:31,310
for living.

34
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,440
From a hundred meters high,

35
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:35,840
they have to
land on their softest bellies.

36
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:37,840
Only the survivors can grow up.

37
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,810
What about the adult birds?

38
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,720
Do they just watch the little birds jump?

39
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,880
They just watch.

40
00:03:45,370 --> 00:03:47,700
This is a lesson for every Barnacle Goose.

41
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,310
But on second thought,

42
00:03:49,310 --> 00:03:51,470
they all survive on their own courage.

43
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:53,430
So, they will always just be themselves,

44
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:55,160
not someone else's appendage.

45
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:57,310
One day, they will stand high up

46
00:03:57,310 --> 00:03:59,910
and look down on the abyss
they once conquered.

47
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,470
I kindly told you a story.

48
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:18,079
Are you secretly cursing me in your heart?

49
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,510
[Xu Miyu, 18th floor,
Daily shift, Bad Review]

50
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:15,560
Miyu.

51
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,850
Where did you go?

52
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:20,430
[Employee Schedule] [Staff Score]

53
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,720
I...

54
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,450
I had an emergency just now.

55
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:27,190
You accompanied your parents, right?

56
00:05:27,190 --> 00:05:28,220
I heard

57
00:05:28,390 --> 00:05:30,270
even the security guards were called.

58
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,930
That was a misunderstanding.

59
00:05:32,150 --> 00:05:33,800
It's fine now.

60
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,159
Is it even a guess?

61
00:05:42,159 --> 00:05:43,950
It must be her parents.

62
00:05:43,970 --> 00:05:45,510
As an adult, she even has to

63
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:48,950
ask her parents to
beat the mistress of her husband.

64
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:50,680
She lives such a cowardly life.

65
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,510
Miyu.

66
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:55,070
The guest has checked out?

67
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:55,800
He just left.

68
00:05:56,950 --> 00:05:59,190
The one who came to beat the mistress
wasn't my biological father,

69
00:05:59,190 --> 00:06:00,380
but my stepfather.

70
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,490
And

71
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,950
if you have any gossip
you want to ask about,

72
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:05,950
I'm right here.

73
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:07,070
No need to guess wildly.

74
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:08,390
You can ask me directly.

75
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:10,270
Miyu, I wasn't talking about you.

76
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:33,230
Starting from the bottom

77
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:35,310
may seem like a detour.

78
00:06:35,450 --> 00:06:36,930
But taking it step by step

79
00:06:36,950 --> 00:06:38,610
might be more down-to-earth.

80
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,870
So, they will always just be themselves,

81
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:42,130
not someone else's appendage.

82
00:06:42,130 --> 00:06:43,860
He holds a black card

83
00:06:43,890 --> 00:06:45,240
and stays on our executive floor.

84
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,450
His judgement

85
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:49,200
carries a lot of weight.

86
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:11,650
Room service.

87
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:18,510
Good morning, Mr. Ji.

88
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:20,750
Is it convenient for me to come in

89
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:22,410
and clean the room for you now?

90
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:24,160
Then, I will start working.

91
00:07:41,190 --> 00:07:42,390
If you find it noisy,

92
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:43,920
please wait in the bedroom first.

93
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,159
I will clean your room
as quickly as possible.

94
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,720
What are you doing?

95
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,720
I'm cleaning.

96
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:51,159
Can you be normal?

97
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,159
Yes, sir.

98
00:07:54,270 --> 00:07:54,920
Okay.

99
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:22,160
Mr. Ji,

100
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:24,360
is there anything else you need me to do?

101
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:26,430
You can leave after cleaning.

102
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:40,030
Didn't I tell you to leave?

103
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:41,909
I see you've been busy all morning.

104
00:08:41,909 --> 00:08:44,570
You may need a cup of coffee
to refresh yourself.

105
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:49,200
My work is my own business.

106
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:50,970
You've finished your work.

107
00:08:50,970 --> 00:08:51,970
You can leave now.

108
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:52,720
Thank you.

109
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,390
You can go.

110
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,720
Mr. Ji,

111
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,270
are you satisfied with my service?

112
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:03,150
If the answer is yes,

113
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,240
please give me a good review.

114
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:04,870
Thank you.

115
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,690
Why should I give you a good review?

116
00:09:09,630 --> 00:09:10,120
Your good review

117
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,870
is the greatest encouragement for my work.

118
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:12,720
Thank you.

119
00:09:15,860 --> 00:09:18,120
Are you playing tricks again?

120
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:23,200
I... I haven't played any tricks.

121
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:27,000
Last time at the birthday banquet
of Nie Yucheng's mother,

122
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,550
my napkin fell on the floor,

123
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,870
and I saw you under the table.

124
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,840
That was a special situation.

125
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,630
And justifiable, right?

126
00:09:39,510 --> 00:09:40,440
Mr. Ji,

127
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:42,630
after you chatted with me last time,

128
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:44,440
I thought you were absolutely right.

129
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,630
I should set a new goal

130
00:09:45,630 --> 00:09:47,090
for my life.

131
00:09:47,110 --> 00:09:48,120
So,

132
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:50,350
my current goal is to be a good attendant

133
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:51,960
and get good reviews from guests.

134
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,870
Isn't your goal a bit too small?

135
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,910
Then, do you think

136
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:58,480
setting my goal as
being the hotel general manager

137
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,680
is easier to achieve?

138
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,320
I... I just think

139
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,720
I was too eager to start over

140
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,960
and too impatient.

141
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:10,440
Now I just want to take it step by step

142
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,320
and do everything well at the moment.

143
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,320
I want to start with

144
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:15,450
getting a good review from you, Mr. Ji.

145
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:20,960
Your service is merely okay at best.

146
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:24,200
It's far from my standard
for a good review.

147
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,840
Then, what is your standard?

148
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:32,960
I... I sincerely want to ask you, Mr. Ji.

149
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,200
Can you tell me

150
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,480
the weakness

151
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,960
of my service?

152
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:38,550
You are over time.

153
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,240
The standard time

154
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:41,630
for cleaning a room is 20 minutes.

155
00:10:41,630 --> 00:10:44,320
You can only be meticulous
within 15 minutes.

156
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:45,550
In the remaining five minutes,

157
00:10:45,550 --> 00:10:47,330
you have to do the final check.

158
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,600
And the time you've spent in my room

159
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:52,010
has been 23 minutes.

160
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:56,320
I think there's a flaw in your standard.

161
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,080
What flaw?

162
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:58,960
The presidential suite upstairs

163
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,440
covers 308 square meters.

164
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,720
Cleaning it completely

165
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,500
requires at least 30 minutes.

166
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:05,080
Each room on the executive floor

167
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,960
averages 78 square meters.

168
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:09,150
It takes at least 25 minutes to clean.

169
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:10,240
I think our service

170
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,600
shouldn't just pursue speed.

171
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:14,130
What's more important
is the service result.

172
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:15,550
Then, let me make one thing clear to you.

173
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:17,790
You are cleaning a guest's room

174
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:18,990
but not your own home.

175
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:21,150
Ensuring both efficiency and quality

176
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:23,050
is the basic quality

177
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,480
of a hotel service staff.

178
00:11:25,170 --> 00:11:26,170
If you can't do it,

179
00:11:26,220 --> 00:11:27,060
I suggest you

180
00:11:27,090 --> 00:11:27,720
go back

181
00:11:27,740 --> 00:11:30,270
and improve
your professional skills first.

182
00:11:30,870 --> 00:11:32,840
I can finish my work

183
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,870
within the specified time.

184
00:11:33,870 --> 00:11:35,550
I just want to provide guests
with more meticulous

185
00:11:35,550 --> 00:11:36,150
and thoughtful service.

186
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:36,840
Then, do you know

187
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:39,040
what the first principle of service is?

188
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,550
To provide guests with the most...

189
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:42,720
It's not to disturb.

190
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:49,720
Then,

191
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:52,440
I won't disturb you.

192
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:01,000
Good review.

193
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,030
Good review.

194
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:10,590
Good review.

195
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:13,610
Do you think I want to disturb you?

196
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,430
I didn't give you a good review,

197
00:12:19,430 --> 00:12:20,690
so you maliciously retaliated against me,
right?

198
00:12:20,690 --> 00:12:21,290
I...

199
00:12:22,490 --> 00:12:24,100
I didn't mean it.

200
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,390
Miyu.

201
00:12:42,250 --> 00:12:44,710
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

202
00:12:44,270 --> 00:12:46,200
I got your dorm address,

203
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,530
so I came to wait for you.

204
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,840
Why did you just get off work?

205
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:51,070
What do you want to do?

206
00:12:52,030 --> 00:12:53,870
I've been cleaning up
the house these days.

207
00:12:53,870 --> 00:12:55,150
There are some of your things.

208
00:12:55,150 --> 00:12:56,480
When Zhenzhen was cleaning,

209
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:57,610
I saved them for you.

210
00:12:57,630 --> 00:12:58,390
The things I didn't take away

211
00:12:58,390 --> 00:12:59,870
are the things I don't want.

212
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:01,070
Just throw them away.

213
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:04,970
I'm here today

214
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,890
to visit you specifically.

215
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:09,150
Although we can't be a couple,

216
00:13:09,150 --> 00:13:11,630
we've been together
for over a decade after all.

217
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:13,000
We can still be friends, right?

218
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,270
There's no need to be so distant.

219
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:15,750
There are some thick clothes inside.

220
00:13:14,350 --> 00:13:15,680
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

221
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:16,630
Winter is coming.

222
00:13:16,630 --> 00:13:17,830
It's cold in the dorm.

223
00:13:18,630 --> 00:13:19,510
Just keep them.

224
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:21,360
I don't want to see you

225
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,160
having a hard time because of me.

226
00:13:30,420 --> 00:13:32,670
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

227
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:34,290
Why did you throw them away?

228
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,270
Nie Yucheng.

229
00:13:36,810 --> 00:13:38,750
Do you think a few words

230
00:13:38,750 --> 00:13:40,150
can trick me back?

231
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:43,600
-No.
-I'm ready to sue you.

232
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:45,680
What did you say?

233
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:47,000
You still owe me four million yuan.

234
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,860
You haven't forgotten, have you?

235
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:50,240
I've made myself very clear to your lawyer

236
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:51,750
about the whereabouts of the money.

237
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:53,000
I don't have 4 million.

238
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,080
Don't go too far.

239
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,120
You know very well

240
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,980
whether you have 4 million or not.

241
00:13:57,270 --> 00:13:59,000
We're going to court anyway.

242
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,720
The law will give me justice.

243
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:02,200
What justice?

244
00:14:03,030 --> 00:14:04,030
Every penny in this family

245
00:14:04,030 --> 00:14:05,790
was earned by me working my fingers
to the bone.

246
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:06,870
I've supported you for so many years.

247
00:14:06,870 --> 00:14:08,390
I bought you everything you have.

248
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:09,320
What have you done for me?

249
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,390
What have you done for this family?

250
00:14:10,390 --> 00:14:11,750
How dare you ask me for money?

251
00:14:11,750 --> 00:14:12,870
Do you have any shame?

252
00:14:12,870 --> 00:14:14,270
You're shameless!

253
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,150
Nie Yucheng,

254
00:14:16,870 --> 00:14:18,390
you've finally stopped acting.

255
00:14:18,390 --> 00:14:19,550
Have you lost your memory?

256
00:14:19,550 --> 00:14:21,320
We've been married for ten years.

257
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:23,750
I did all the housework for a whole decade

258
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:26,030
and took care of you 24/7.

259
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:28,120
Even if you hire a nanny,
you have to pay her.

260
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:28,790
Also,

261
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:30,390
as your wife,

262
00:14:30,510 --> 00:14:32,670
I maintained your business relationships,

263
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:33,720
curried favor with others,

264
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:34,630
and helped you sign those orders

265
00:14:34,630 --> 00:14:36,440
worthy hundreds of thousands
or millions.

266
00:14:34,740 --> 00:14:36,360
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

267
00:14:36,470 --> 00:14:38,510
Now they are all the credit of you alone,
huh?

268
00:14:38,510 --> 00:14:39,790
Where is my salary?

269
00:14:39,790 --> 00:14:41,150
Xu Miyu, you…

270
00:14:41,150 --> 00:14:43,280
I'm going to make it clear to you today.

271
00:14:43,670 --> 00:14:45,200
I will go to court,

272
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,740
and I will definitely win.

273
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:49,550
This money belongs to the former Xu Miyu,

274
00:14:50,030 --> 00:14:51,630
and I will get it back for her.

275
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:54,880
Now that you love money so much,

276
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,890
why were you so eager to divorce me?

277
00:14:57,030 --> 00:14:58,690
You should have known better.

278
00:14:58,790 --> 00:15:00,410
If you were still Mrs. Nie,

279
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,970
all my money would be yours.

280
00:15:03,670 --> 00:15:05,130
Even now,

281
00:15:05,550 --> 00:15:08,790
do you still think I care
about your money?

282
00:15:24,550 --> 00:15:26,200
Honey, you're back.

283
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:27,510
I'm back.

284
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:30,200
Did you buy this takeout?

285
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,170
Yes.

286
00:15:32,390 --> 00:15:33,650
This is our dinner.

287
00:15:34,870 --> 00:15:36,200
Look, does it look good?

288
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:38,200
I plan to wear this on my first day
of work tomorrow.

289
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,270
It looks good.

290
00:15:39,270 --> 00:15:40,150
So beautiful.

291
00:15:40,790 --> 00:15:41,990
You didn't even look.

292
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:43,080
You're so perfunctory.

293
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,870
Let me have a look.

294
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:45,790
Come on.

295
00:15:45,790 --> 00:15:47,250
Turn around and let me see.

296
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:50,720
My wife looks good in everything.

297
00:15:51,030 --> 00:15:52,630
You're so sweet-talking.

298
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:54,910
Did you throw away
what I asked you to throw?

299
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:56,440
I threw them away.

300
00:15:56,510 --> 00:15:57,440
Why would I lie to you?

301
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,550
Not necessarily.

302
00:15:58,750 --> 00:16:00,390
You never tell the truth.

303
00:16:02,670 --> 00:16:03,870
My wife

304
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:06,670
is the woman who treats me best
in the world.

305
00:16:06,910 --> 00:16:09,030
I swear all my money

306
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:11,200
and everything, including myself,

307
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,660
belong to you and the baby.

308
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:15,210
I will definitely give you happiness.

309
00:16:16,030 --> 00:16:17,030
What's up?

310
00:16:17,150 --> 00:16:18,030
Nothing.

311
00:16:18,270 --> 00:16:18,790
I suddenly realized

312
00:16:18,790 --> 00:16:20,920
that I haven't said these words to you.

313
00:16:21,870 --> 00:16:22,720
Okay then.

314
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:25,080
You drop me off
at Purong for work tomorrow.

315
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:25,920
Okay.

316
00:16:49,590 --> 00:16:53,660
[Purong Hotel]

317
00:16:57,260 --> 00:16:58,720
Mr. Ray, this way, please.

318
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:00,550
Hello.

319
00:17:00,550 --> 00:17:01,840
I'm new in the sales department.

320
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:02,960
I'm Lu Zhenzhen.

321
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:03,670
Director Lu.

322
00:17:03,670 --> 00:17:06,069
Mr. Feng told me specifically this morning

323
00:17:06,069 --> 00:17:08,440
that a newly transferred supervisor
from the sales department

324
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:10,720
brought a major client
to our executive floor,

325
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,310
and asked us to treat him well.

326
00:17:12,310 --> 00:17:13,329
This is...

327
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,310
This is Mr. Ray.

328
00:17:15,310 --> 00:17:16,829
He came from Malaysia to Shanghai

329
00:17:16,829 --> 00:17:19,440
as a cultural tourism commissioner
for a special inspection.

330
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:20,349
Hello, sir.

331
00:17:20,349 --> 00:17:23,010
Welcome to the executive floor
of Purong Hotel.

332
00:17:23,030 --> 00:17:24,440
I will check you in now.

333
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:26,310
Please show your ID.

334
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,200
Ms. Zhang,

335
00:17:35,740 --> 00:17:36,940
Mr. Ray

336
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:38,070
is in charge of

337
00:17:38,070 --> 00:17:39,720
corporate legal conferences in Malaysia.

338
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,830
Throughout Southeast Asia,

339
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:42,680
he has a lot of conference resources.

340
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:45,010
Please make sure you take good care
of him this time.

341
00:17:45,010 --> 00:17:46,810
If he has a good stay experience,

342
00:17:47,070 --> 00:17:48,550
we will have many big orders.

343
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:50,960
This is a new batch of aromatherapy
from our sales department.

344
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:52,560
I'll give you a bottle to try.

345
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,200
Director Lu,

346
00:17:54,590 --> 00:17:56,070
you are too kind.

347
00:17:56,070 --> 00:17:56,830
Don't worry.

348
00:17:57,070 --> 00:17:59,030
We will definitely use
the highest standards

349
00:17:59,030 --> 00:18:00,270
to receive your VIP.

350
00:18:00,310 --> 00:18:02,170
Please take good care of him then.

351
00:18:02,270 --> 00:18:03,600
Call Luo Qingping over.

352
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:04,960
No need.

353
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:06,070
Let it be her.

354
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:12,810
This attendant is a newcomer.

355
00:18:12,810 --> 00:18:14,790
I'm afraid her service
might not be perfect.

356
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:17,120
Newcomers need opportunities even more.

357
00:18:17,550 --> 00:18:18,480
Let her serve me.

358
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:22,510
Miyu.

359
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:24,720
Ms. Zhang.

360
00:18:26,830 --> 00:18:29,230
You are responsible for this guest's room.

361
00:18:33,270 --> 00:18:34,480
Glad to serve you.

362
00:18:35,070 --> 00:18:35,590
Mr. Ray

363
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:37,240
is a major client of our sales department.

364
00:18:37,240 --> 00:18:38,840
Please take good care of him.

365
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:42,830
I'll do it myself.

366
00:18:44,510 --> 00:18:45,550
The opportunity is given to you.

367
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:46,830
I hope you cherish it.

368
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:49,310
You must be tired from the journey.

369
00:18:49,310 --> 00:18:50,310
Let me do it.

370
00:18:50,830 --> 00:18:51,830
This way, please.

371
00:18:57,110 --> 00:18:59,310
Director Lu, rest assured.

372
00:18:59,310 --> 00:19:01,070
We will provide excellent service

373
00:19:01,070 --> 00:19:04,070
and cooperate seamlessly
with the sales department.

374
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:17,080
Let me open the door for you.

375
00:19:20,790 --> 00:19:21,650
Please come in.

376
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:24,640
Miss,

377
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:26,090
can I have your WeChat?

378
00:19:26,550 --> 00:19:27,640
I'm sorry, sir.

379
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,590
Our hotel has a rule

380
00:19:28,590 --> 00:19:30,640
that we can't add guests' contact
information without permission.

381
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:31,920
If you have any needs,

382
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:33,830
dial the phone by the bed.

383
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,750
I just think you are very nice.

384
00:19:35,830 --> 00:19:37,160
I hope during my stay,

385
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:38,820
you will be the one serving me.

386
00:19:40,310 --> 00:19:40,920
I'm sorry.

387
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:42,240
I have to follow our rule.

388
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,590
In other hotels,

389
00:19:43,830 --> 00:19:45,830
the butlers would give me
their contact information.

390
00:19:45,830 --> 00:19:47,030
Is Purong

391
00:19:47,310 --> 00:19:49,310
being a bit disrespectful to
the guests?

392
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:50,570
Then I won't stay here.

393
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,810
I'll change to a hotel
with better service.

394
00:19:52,810 --> 00:19:53,730
Sir,

395
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:55,640
let me add your contact.

396
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:02,590
Just let me know if you need anything.

397
00:20:07,170 --> 00:20:08,400
Just tell me,

398
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:10,270
is the big boss of Kuanli coming?

399
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:11,310
Yeah.

400
00:20:11,310 --> 00:20:11,830
Exactly.

401
00:20:11,830 --> 00:20:13,640
Stop guessing.

402
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:15,070
Do you know the scale of Kuanli?

403
00:20:15,070 --> 00:20:16,400
The big boss of Kuanli, Duan Longyun,

404
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:18,830
manages dozens of companies nationwide.

405
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,070
If he really stayed upstairs,

406
00:20:20,070 --> 00:20:22,000
who would manage those companies?

407
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:25,830
But there's definitely a reason
for keeping you busy.

408
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:28,310
He's not the only Boss Duan
in Kuanli Group.

409
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:31,070
Could it be the younger Boss Duan,
Duan Aoxiang?

410
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:32,110
I never said that.

411
00:20:32,110 --> 00:20:33,270
It's him.

412
00:20:33,270 --> 00:20:34,350
I really like him.

413
00:20:34,350 --> 00:20:35,480
Me too.

414
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:37,550
He's both a noble gentleman
and a popular star.

415
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:38,880
I really like him too.

416
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,480
Look at you all.

417
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:41,340
Let me tell you,

418
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:42,060
Mr. Duan Jr.

419
00:20:42,090 --> 00:20:43,310
has a master's degree

420
00:20:43,310 --> 00:20:44,480
in hotel management

421
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:45,550
from the University of Birmingham.

422
00:20:45,550 --> 00:20:47,750
The gambling agreement
with Purong Hotel

423
00:20:47,750 --> 00:20:49,550
is a project he led.

424
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:51,440
Maybe in a year,

425
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:52,880
he will be your boss.

426
00:20:59,070 --> 00:20:59,750
Sir,

427
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:02,210
this place has been booked out.

428
00:21:09,110 --> 00:21:09,880
Sir,

429
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:13,480
this place has also been booked out.

430
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:15,510
This is a public area.

431
00:21:15,510 --> 00:21:16,680
How can it be booked out?

432
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:17,550
Besides,

433
00:21:17,550 --> 00:21:18,720
in the time you're stopping me,

434
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:20,110
I could have finished a cup of coffee.

435
00:21:20,110 --> 00:21:20,830
Actually,

436
00:21:20,830 --> 00:21:22,110
the VIP will arrive at any time.

437
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:22,720
How about you go...

438
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:24,510
I said this is a public area.

439
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:26,120
Don't you understand me?

440
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:27,240
I understand.

441
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:29,480
Do you always drive away
all the guests in the hotel

442
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:31,030
every time you receive a VIP?

443
00:21:31,030 --> 00:21:32,590
Sorry.

444
00:21:32,790 --> 00:21:33,550
What's up?

445
00:21:34,310 --> 00:21:36,030
Mr. Wei said to clear the area,

446
00:21:36,310 --> 00:21:39,510
but this gentleman insists on
having a cup of coffee here.

447
00:21:40,110 --> 00:21:40,830
Go ahead.

448
00:21:40,830 --> 00:21:41,760
Leave this to me.

449
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:53,370
You can't recognize me, right?

450
00:21:54,750 --> 00:21:56,030
Indeed, I can't.

451
00:21:57,720 --> 00:21:58,520
I grew up ugly.

452
00:22:03,110 --> 00:22:04,160
Senior Xue Rui.

453
00:22:06,310 --> 00:22:07,920
Long time no see.

454
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,660
How many years has it been?

455
00:22:14,830 --> 00:22:15,830
Ten years, right?

456
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:16,960
Ten years.

457
00:22:19,770 --> 00:22:20,720
Come, leader.

458
00:22:20,720 --> 00:22:22,550
Xue, pour the wine.

459
00:22:23,750 --> 00:22:25,110
Mr. Liu,

460
00:22:25,750 --> 00:22:28,610
thank you for your bank's great support
for my work.

461
00:22:28,760 --> 00:22:30,310
I toast you.

462
00:22:30,310 --> 00:22:31,110
Chug!
You can drink as much as you want.

463
00:22:31,110 --> 00:22:32,070
Come on.

464
00:22:32,470 --> 00:22:33,270
Please.

465
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:37,070
Good.

466
00:22:37,070 --> 00:22:37,970
Good drinker.

467
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:42,750
Come on.

468
00:22:42,260 --> 00:22:43,370
[Young Xue Rui]

469
00:22:42,750 --> 00:22:43,830
Everyone, cheers.

470
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:45,070
Thank you for coming. Come on.

471
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:45,640
Xue, come on.

472
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:46,310
Pour the drinks.

473
00:22:46,310 --> 00:22:46,830
Hurry.

474
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:48,750
Come on.

475
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,400
Thank you all.

476
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:51,720
Let's continue to cooperate.

477
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:52,510
Come on, together.

478
00:22:52,510 --> 00:22:53,000
Cheers. Come on.

479
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:54,920
Thanks to your help
back then, senior.

480
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:57,270
Or I would be kicked out as a rookie.

481
00:22:57,300 --> 00:22:59,700
Thanks to you, I completed the internship.

482
00:23:00,270 --> 00:23:03,070
In the blink of an eye,
the rookie has become a boss.

483
00:23:03,760 --> 00:23:04,460
By the way.

484
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:06,790
I remember you've been abroad.

485
00:23:06,790 --> 00:23:08,050
When did you come back?

486
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,350
Not long ago.

487
00:23:11,030 --> 00:23:12,230
What brings you here?

488
00:23:12,270 --> 00:23:13,400
First,

489
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:15,720
take a vacation and rest.

490
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:20,160
Do you want to go to my office?

491
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:22,030
Director Xue.

492
00:23:22,550 --> 00:23:23,160
Coming.

493
00:23:23,270 --> 00:23:25,480
Mr. Wei asked us
to gather at the VIP channel.

494
00:23:25,480 --> 00:23:26,270
Hurry up.

495
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:26,880
Okay.

496
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:28,030
How about this?

497
00:23:28,030 --> 00:23:28,550
I'll get back to work.

498
00:23:28,550 --> 00:23:30,480
I'll find you after I'm done today.

499
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,480
I have a big family here.

500
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:34,640
How are we supposed to move?

501
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:35,880
We will help you pack.

502
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:37,030
You just need to move.

503
00:23:37,030 --> 00:23:38,350
We can give you a discount
on the room rate,

504
00:23:38,350 --> 00:23:40,210
a 50% discount. What do you think?

505
00:23:40,480 --> 00:23:41,750
A 50% discount?

506
00:23:43,030 --> 00:23:44,440
Can you make it a 60% discount?

507
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,480
I'm sorry, sir.

508
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:47,440
This price is set by our director.

509
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:50,400
Hello, room service.

510
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:53,160
Hello, Mr. Ji.

511
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:55,240
Mr. Ji.

512
00:23:57,110 --> 00:23:58,200
He's dead asleep?

513
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:03,550
Who are you talking about?

514
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:04,570
Mr. Ji,

515
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:06,820
is it okay for you to
change to a new room?

516
00:24:06,820 --> 00:24:08,440
The subsequent room rate will be 50% off.

517
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,700
Why do I need to change?

518
00:24:10,960 --> 00:24:12,510
The water pipe
on the executive floor is broken.

519
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:14,680
The Engineering Department
needs to repair it.

520
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:15,480
Where is it broken?

521
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:16,750
Take me to see it.

522
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:19,720
That's the Engineering
Department's business.

523
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:22,160
We attendants are only responsible
for communication.

524
00:24:22,160 --> 00:24:23,270
That's nonsense.

525
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:27,130
Then when is it convenient
for you to change to a new room?

526
00:24:28,350 --> 00:24:30,680
When is it convenient for you, please?

527
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:33,940
Watch out, I'll complain about you
disturbing the guests.

528
00:24:37,350 --> 00:24:38,160
What are you doing?

529
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:39,350
This is my job.

530
00:24:39,350 --> 00:24:40,710
Find someone else to talk to me.

531
00:24:40,710 --> 00:24:41,400
Move aside.

532
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,790
The renovation concept of Purong Hotel is

533
00:24:56,790 --> 00:24:57,480
sharpness.

534
00:24:57,920 --> 00:25:00,240
Radormok white marble

535
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:02,070
paired with black agate and pure gold

536
00:25:02,070 --> 00:25:03,240
seems bright and noble,

537
00:25:02,170 --> 00:25:04,440
[Lobby area]

538
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:04,270
and magnificent.

539
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:10,620
[Space Design]

540
00:25:04,510 --> 00:25:06,030
As for the original crystal
lighting of Purong,

541
00:25:06,030 --> 00:25:07,350
we have kept it.

542
00:25:07,350 --> 00:25:08,480
But for things like

543
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:11,590
the complicated geometric splicing
on the walls,

544
00:25:11,590 --> 00:25:12,270
we will consider

545
00:25:12,270 --> 00:25:14,960
replacing it with large blocks
of color later.

546
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:17,400
Then, what's the difference
between this and

547
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:19,030
the Kuanli Dinghui Resort Hotel

548
00:25:19,030 --> 00:25:20,440
we built in Shenzhen before?

549
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:21,440
Mr. Duan, this...

550
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:23,370
It doesn't sound very innovative.

551
00:25:23,720 --> 00:25:25,030
Innovation...

552
00:25:25,030 --> 00:25:26,490
The innovation lies in...

553
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:32,200
Sorry.

554
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:33,200
I didn't hear you.

555
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:37,040
The innovation lies in the difference
in internal modeling.

556
00:25:40,270 --> 00:25:41,270
What I want is

557
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:42,350
very simple.

558
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:45,640
Mr. Duan,

559
00:25:45,640 --> 00:25:48,240
only what hasn't been seen
before is shocking.

560
00:25:48,920 --> 00:25:50,620
Tell your boss later.

561
00:25:50,750 --> 00:25:52,880
Stop fooling me with ideas
from ten years ago.

562
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:53,640
Okay.

563
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:54,720
I will go back and report.

564
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:56,160
We make a new design for you.

565
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,480
That's your business.

566
00:25:59,790 --> 00:26:00,680
Are you hungry?

567
00:26:02,790 --> 00:26:03,390
Let's go.

568
00:26:11,270 --> 00:26:13,110
-Mr. Duan.
-Mr. Duan.

569
00:26:13,110 --> 00:26:15,160
-Mr. Duan Jr.
-Mr. Duan Jr.

570
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:19,200
Welcome.

571
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:22,640
I specially reserved
the presidential suite for you,

572
00:26:22,640 --> 00:26:23,640
is it okay?

573
00:26:23,750 --> 00:26:26,000
Only you have the qualification
to stay in the suite.

574
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:27,750
Is it the suite where
the president has stayed?

575
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:29,480
I'm enjoying the honor, huh?

576
00:26:30,590 --> 00:26:31,310
By the way,

577
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:34,270
hurry up with the supplementary agreement.

578
00:26:34,270 --> 00:26:35,530
You haven't signed it.

579
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:36,720
I'm afraid that there will be changes.

580
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:38,720
You must be joking. How would I dare?

581
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:41,490
It's just that the details
still need to be refined.

582
00:26:41,490 --> 00:26:43,200
As long as you don't change your mind,

583
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,960
I am absolutely loyal.

584
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:45,640
That's good.

585
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:46,790
And there is the same issue

586
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:47,720
I've mentioned.

587
00:26:47,720 --> 00:26:49,510
Everything that can be solved with money

588
00:26:49,510 --> 00:26:50,200
is not a big deal.

589
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:52,160
I understand. I know this.

590
00:26:52,160 --> 00:26:53,750
Mr. Duan.

591
00:26:54,420 --> 00:26:56,020
Just one minute of your time.

592
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:58,150
The executive floor has been cleared.

593
00:26:58,200 --> 00:26:59,080
But...

594
00:26:59,110 --> 00:26:59,920
But what?

595
00:27:00,270 --> 00:27:01,720
Didn't I say to waive all bills?

596
00:27:01,720 --> 00:27:03,480
I did so.

597
00:27:04,110 --> 00:27:06,480
The other guests all happily moved out.

598
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:07,960
Only one person is left.

599
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:09,510
Then give him a large amount of money.

600
00:27:09,510 --> 00:27:12,200
Everything that can be solved with money
is not a big deal.

601
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,000
Yes, I know.

602
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:16,230
But this person probably
doesn't want money.

603
00:27:16,350 --> 00:27:17,640
Who?

604
00:27:17,640 --> 00:27:18,350
Who is it?

605
00:27:18,350 --> 00:27:19,480
You can't handle it?

606
00:27:20,790 --> 00:27:21,920
Doesn't want money?

607
00:27:22,160 --> 00:27:22,960
Interesting.

608
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:26,240
Then I'll go meet this tough nut.

609
00:27:45,240 --> 00:27:46,170
Hello, Mr. Duan.

610
00:27:48,510 --> 00:27:49,440
Hello, Mr. Duan.

611
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:00,410
Hello, Mr. Duan.

612
00:28:09,830 --> 00:28:10,640
Sir,

613
00:28:10,640 --> 00:28:12,840
please cooperate and change your room.

614
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:14,830
Who are you?

615
00:28:14,830 --> 00:28:15,680
As for money,

616
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,680
you can make any demands you want.

617
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:20,400
Are you from the Engineering Department

618
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:22,400
or another department of the hotel?

619
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:25,820
If you are not hotel staff,

620
00:28:25,820 --> 00:28:27,670
you have no right to talk
to me about this.

621
00:28:27,670 --> 00:28:28,670
Wait.

622
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,590
Don't you recognize me?

623
00:28:35,270 --> 00:28:36,750
Mr. Duan is here.

624
00:28:36,750 --> 00:28:39,200
I thought it was some young punk

625
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:41,400
who didn't know his place
trying to mess with me.

626
00:28:41,400 --> 00:28:42,680
So, it's you after all.

627
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:45,030
If you want to meet me, just contact me.

628
00:28:45,110 --> 00:28:46,590
Why put on such a big show

629
00:28:46,590 --> 00:28:47,960
and have so many people
play along with you?

630
00:28:47,960 --> 00:28:49,560
Mr. Duan, you like a big show,

631
00:28:49,840 --> 00:28:52,440
so the welcome gift should
cater to your taste.

632
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:56,440
Old classmate,

633
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:57,610
I missed you so much.

634
00:28:59,270 --> 00:28:59,720
This is

635
00:28:59,720 --> 00:29:01,790
my classmate and

636
00:29:01,790 --> 00:29:02,590
my good buddy in Birmingham.

637
00:29:02,590 --> 00:29:03,310
Call him Mr. Ji.

638
00:29:03,310 --> 00:29:04,920
Hello, Mr. Ji.

639
00:29:05,540 --> 00:29:06,960
Such a big show.

640
00:29:06,960 --> 00:29:08,960
Are they celebrating downstairs?

641
00:29:09,580 --> 00:29:11,110
What is there to celebrate?

642
00:29:14,030 --> 00:29:16,570
What do you think I'm celebrating?

643
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:19,270
Kuanli Group invested in Purong Hotel

644
00:29:19,270 --> 00:29:20,790
and reached a strategic partnership?

645
00:29:20,790 --> 00:29:22,070
This is all trending.

646
00:29:22,310 --> 00:29:24,240
It's not surprising to celebrate.

647
00:29:24,610 --> 00:29:25,630
It seems

648
00:29:25,750 --> 00:29:27,170
you really don't know anything.

649
00:29:27,170 --> 00:29:28,640
I was never part of this to begin with.

650
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:29,980
You're no outsider.

651
00:29:30,010 --> 00:29:31,310
You are my best buddy

652
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:32,150
from my time in Birmingham.

653
00:29:32,150 --> 00:29:32,830
Let's go.

654
00:29:32,830 --> 00:29:34,030
Join the fun with me.

655
00:29:34,550 --> 00:29:36,550
Does the water pipe need to be fixed?

656
00:29:37,030 --> 00:29:38,480
Still got a sharp tongue.

657
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:39,350
We're not fixing it.

658
00:29:39,350 --> 00:29:40,400
Even if we did,

659
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:42,200
we'd skip your room,

660
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,270
okay? Let's go.

661
00:29:43,810 --> 00:29:44,490
Wait.

662
00:29:44,790 --> 00:29:45,960
You're in a suit.

663
00:29:45,960 --> 00:29:47,000
I need to change.

664
00:29:47,440 --> 00:29:48,450
It's a celebration banquet.

665
00:29:48,450 --> 00:29:49,380
You've changed.

666
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:52,070
But I like it more and more.

667
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:54,640
Hurry up, I'll wait for you.

668
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:55,440
Okay.

669
00:30:04,510 --> 00:30:07,240
You two will go help
in the executive lounge today.

670
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:07,880
I am a newcomer.

671
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:09,310
I'm not very familiar with

672
00:30:09,310 --> 00:30:11,000
the service process
of the executive lounge yet.

673
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,110
It's okay.

674
00:30:12,110 --> 00:30:14,270
You work carefully
and have a good attitude.

675
00:30:14,270 --> 00:30:15,800
You'll definitely be fine.

676
00:30:16,510 --> 00:30:17,200
But I...

677
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:18,270
Let me tell you.

678
00:30:18,270 --> 00:30:20,980
All the guests on the spot today are VIPs.

679
00:30:21,070 --> 00:30:22,640
If you can get

680
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:23,720
a good review from them,

681
00:30:23,720 --> 00:30:24,790
your two bad reviews

682
00:30:24,790 --> 00:30:27,110
might be offset.

683
00:30:43,270 --> 00:30:45,270
Does he think he is Prince Charming?

684
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:04,070
Thank you.

685
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:11,400
Speak of the devil.

686
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:12,350
Come here.

687
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:15,000
This is

688
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:17,060
Ji Feng, whom I was mentioned before.

689
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:19,440
Ji Feng is my classmate,

690
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:23,640
an all-rounder in hotel management
from the University of Birmingham.

691
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,400
Mr. Wei,

692
00:31:24,790 --> 00:31:25,720
long time no see.

693
00:31:26,310 --> 00:31:27,640
You two know each other?

694
00:31:27,920 --> 00:31:30,030
I used to work at Purong Hotel

695
00:31:30,030 --> 00:31:32,110
and met with
Mr. Wei a few times.

696
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:34,550
You once worked at Purong?

697
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,240
How did I not know that?

698
00:31:36,240 --> 00:31:37,770
It was before I went abroad.

699
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:42,550
I've heard Mr. Duan Jr. say

700
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:44,070
that he has someone very capable with him,

701
00:31:44,070 --> 00:31:47,200
who's been managing
top-tier luxury hotels overseas for years.

702
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:48,590
So, you were talking about Ji Feng.

703
00:31:48,590 --> 00:31:49,070
Yeah.

704
00:31:49,070 --> 00:31:50,600
Then we go way back.

705
00:31:50,790 --> 00:31:53,350
If I were not Mr. Duan's
former classmate,

706
00:31:53,350 --> 00:31:55,110
I wouldn't have gotten in today.

707
00:31:55,110 --> 00:31:56,550
No way, you're joking.

708
00:31:56,550 --> 00:31:58,440
You don't know this, Mr. Duan Jr.

709
00:31:58,440 --> 00:31:59,960
When Ji Feng worked at Purong,

710
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:01,440
he was an outstanding employee.

711
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:03,400
He is capable and popular.

712
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:04,400
I always said

713
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:06,880
he'd be a great talent
in hotel management.

714
00:32:07,030 --> 00:32:09,030
Now that you've got
some overseas experience,

715
00:32:09,030 --> 00:32:11,960
maybe I should be calling you Mr. Ji.

716
00:32:12,590 --> 00:32:13,920
Mr. Wei, you flatter me.

717
00:32:14,030 --> 00:32:15,110
Well, isn't that a coincidence?

718
00:32:15,110 --> 00:32:15,920
Next year,

719
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,730
come be my general manager.

720
00:32:17,920 --> 00:32:19,480
Of what?

721
00:32:19,590 --> 00:32:20,530
Purong.

722
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:23,100
So confident.

723
00:32:23,240 --> 00:32:24,720
Looks like investment
is just the appetizer,

724
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:26,440
and acquisition is the main course.

725
00:32:26,440 --> 00:32:27,110
Smart.

726
00:32:28,030 --> 00:32:29,200
Mr. Duan Jr.,

727
00:32:29,370 --> 00:32:31,140
don't speak too soon.

728
00:32:31,270 --> 00:32:33,550
Although our hotel has
some operational issues,

729
00:32:33,550 --> 00:32:35,030
we still have a year

730
00:32:35,030 --> 00:32:35,960
to turn things around.

731
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,550
Come on, Mr. Wei,

732
00:32:37,550 --> 00:32:38,310
easy.

733
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:39,240
Anyway,

734
00:32:39,240 --> 00:32:40,110
Ji Feng

735
00:32:40,110 --> 00:32:40,960
isn't an outsider either.

736
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:41,720
What are you afraid of?

737
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:42,680
Besides,

738
00:32:42,680 --> 00:32:43,920
handing Purong over to me,

739
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:44,880
you won't lose out.

740
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:45,880
Yes.

741
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:47,030
With you backing it,

742
00:32:47,030 --> 00:32:48,230
what do I have to fear?

743
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:49,700
We're all friends.

744
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:52,640
Well, you guys chat.

745
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:53,720
I have things to do.

746
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:55,500
I'll get going.

747
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:12,030
Look into Ji Feng,

748
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:14,450
and see what he's really back for.

749
00:33:14,550 --> 00:33:15,350
Okay.

750
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:21,510
I heard you left Siwei Group

751
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:25,260
and then swallowed sand for three years.

752
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:26,590
It's good to be back.

753
00:33:26,590 --> 00:33:28,790
There's gold everywhere in our country.

754
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:30,250
Where are you working now?

755
00:33:30,720 --> 00:33:32,310
I didn't make great achievements.

756
00:33:32,310 --> 00:33:33,400
Just slack off for now.

757
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:34,800
You're fooling me again.

758
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:36,480
Actually, when I saw you today,

759
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:38,210
I was thinking about one thing.

760
00:33:38,550 --> 00:33:39,500
Why are you here?

761
00:33:39,790 --> 00:33:40,990
Just take a vacation.

762
00:33:41,310 --> 00:33:43,240
No need to rack your brains over it.

763
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:45,270
Alright then.

764
00:33:46,030 --> 00:33:47,350
After your vacation,

765
00:33:47,350 --> 00:33:48,400
come work for me.

766
00:33:48,830 --> 00:33:50,030
Just name your price.

767
00:33:50,070 --> 00:33:50,640
It's the same to

768
00:33:50,640 --> 00:33:51,570
work for anyone.

769
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:54,410
Mr. Duan, who is this?

770
00:33:54,880 --> 00:33:55,960
Let me introduce.

771
00:33:56,110 --> 00:33:56,720
This is

772
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:59,980
Ji Feng, the top manager of Siwei Group,

773
00:34:00,270 --> 00:34:02,110
and my classmate
when I studied in Birmingham.

774
00:34:02,110 --> 00:34:03,480
Back in school,

775
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:04,680
he was in first place,

776
00:34:04,830 --> 00:34:05,760
and I was second.

777
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:07,110
We

778
00:34:07,110 --> 00:34:09,880
were known as the Dual Heroes
of Birmingham.

779
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:12,050
This nickname combining East and West

780
00:34:12,080 --> 00:34:13,190
isn't very credible.

781
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,880
Don't sabotage my efforts.

782
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:17,280
Don't just stand there.

783
00:34:17,280 --> 00:34:19,360
Let's go taste today's main dish.

784
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:20,400
Let's go.

785
00:34:20,670 --> 00:34:21,360
Let's go.

786
00:34:32,590 --> 00:34:33,550
These were shipped

787
00:34:33,550 --> 00:34:35,679
fresh from Europe early this morning.

788
00:34:43,550 --> 00:34:44,480
Have a taste.

789
00:34:48,150 --> 00:34:49,400
This taste...

790
00:34:54,670 --> 00:34:55,469
It's not good.

791
00:34:55,710 --> 00:34:57,550
Chef, take away all the caviar.

792
00:34:57,670 --> 00:34:58,440
Change it.

793
00:35:03,640 --> 00:35:05,150
Call Li Qiaoqi over here, quick.

794
00:35:05,150 --> 00:35:05,880
Okay.

795
00:35:09,700 --> 00:35:10,530
Qiaoqi,

796
00:35:10,560 --> 00:35:12,110
the guest in the executive lounge upstairs

797
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:13,590
wants you to make a seafood feast.

798
00:35:13,590 --> 00:35:14,400
I'm not going.

799
00:35:14,710 --> 00:35:16,480
With those big boxes of caviar there,

800
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:18,320
they can eat anything with it and be full.

801
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,230
I'll just have some shrimp here.

802
00:35:19,230 --> 00:35:20,000
You have to.

803
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:20,840
Qiaoqi,

804
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:23,550
the boss upstairs said he doesn't want
the caviar feast anymore,

805
00:35:23,550 --> 00:35:26,280
and wants delicacies from land and sea.

806
00:35:26,510 --> 00:35:27,320
What the heck?

807
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:28,650
That's such a long name.

808
00:35:30,440 --> 00:35:32,750
I want to see who's causing trouble.

809
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:33,550
Let's go.

810
00:35:36,030 --> 00:35:37,230
I will definitely

811
00:35:38,230 --> 00:35:39,490
acquire Purong Hotel.

812
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:41,440
Since when did Mr. Duan become

813
00:35:41,440 --> 00:35:42,630
so career-driven?

814
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:44,800
My father

815
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:45,880
finds fault with me every day.

816
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:46,710
He said

817
00:35:46,710 --> 00:35:49,360
if I don't show him
some results this time,

818
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:51,600
he might kick me out of the house one day.

819
00:35:52,230 --> 00:35:53,190
This time,

820
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:54,480
this Purong project

821
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:56,280
was single-handedly dug up by me.

822
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,540
I think this will work.

823
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:02,460
Why did you decide to
deal with such a troublesome case?

824
00:36:02,550 --> 00:36:03,940
Purong Hotel

825
00:36:04,550 --> 00:36:06,840
is a grand old hotel in Shanghai.

826
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:08,710
It just looks strong on the outside.

827
00:36:08,710 --> 00:36:10,840
Go look at their financial report
from last year.

828
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:12,550
They had a loss of 47 percent.

829
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:13,550
If they want to

830
00:36:13,550 --> 00:36:16,320
make a 30 percent profit within a year,

831
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:18,200
achieving an 80 percent growth,

832
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:19,530
they need a miracle.

833
00:36:21,070 --> 00:36:21,880
Trust me.

834
00:36:22,230 --> 00:36:23,360
Purong Hotel

835
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:25,230
will definitely be mine in a year.

836
00:36:25,630 --> 00:36:26,360
No suspense.

837
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:29,140
Old classmate,

838
00:36:29,660 --> 00:36:31,740
nothing is certain in this world.

839
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:34,510
But you won't lose out either way.

840
00:36:34,510 --> 00:36:36,240
Even if you don't get the hotel,

841
00:36:36,240 --> 00:36:38,030
you still get a high return rate
in one year.

842
00:36:38,030 --> 00:36:38,710
You make a lot of money too.

843
00:36:38,710 --> 00:36:40,120
Who cares about this little money?

844
00:36:40,120 --> 00:36:41,480
What I want is the entire hotel,

845
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:42,560
the whole building.

846
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:43,850
Just for

847
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:46,030
that Presidential Suite,
where a few presidents have stayed,

848
00:36:46,030 --> 00:36:47,340
I must get it.

849
00:36:47,670 --> 00:36:48,760
When the time comes,

850
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:49,890
you can work with me,

851
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:52,220
and we will create brilliance together.

852
00:36:52,220 --> 00:36:53,260
It's a deal,

853
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:55,160
no going back.

854
00:37:01,550 --> 00:37:02,550
The person

855
00:37:02,710 --> 00:37:04,150
in the red suit

856
00:37:04,150 --> 00:37:06,070
is Mr. Duan Jr. from the Kuanli Group.

857
00:37:06,070 --> 00:37:07,670
He threw today's party too.

858
00:37:08,190 --> 00:37:09,360
Making last-minute changes

859
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:11,270
was his idea.

860
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,190
I hate these

861
00:37:12,190 --> 00:37:14,720
rich kids whose brains
are soaked in alcohol.

862
00:37:14,760 --> 00:37:16,760
He delayed me from getting off work.

863
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:09,230
Ya, Luo,

864
00:38:14,510 --> 00:38:15,400
thank you.

865
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:17,920
It's delicious.

866
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:19,240
Awesome.

867
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:20,070
Smells good.

868
00:38:20,800 --> 00:38:21,800
BBQ.

869
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:22,860
This is a good idea.

870
00:38:24,320 --> 00:38:25,800
I'll go get some drinks.

871
00:38:37,670 --> 00:38:38,760
Ya.

872
00:38:40,550 --> 00:38:41,550
Come in and get the raw marinated food.

873
00:38:41,550 --> 00:38:42,030
Okay.

874
00:38:45,070 --> 00:38:45,840
Luo.

875
00:38:46,150 --> 00:38:47,000
Come help.

876
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:49,160
Here, take this over.

877
00:38:52,110 --> 00:38:52,550
Hurry up.

878
00:38:52,550 --> 00:38:53,110
Okay.

879
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:15,360
Why is it all gone?

880
00:39:15,510 --> 00:39:17,150
Chef, please make some more.

881
00:39:19,070 --> 00:39:20,440
Sorry, I'm off work.

882
00:39:20,670 --> 00:39:21,960
Ya, let's go.

883
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:22,760
Okay.

884
00:39:30,850 --> 00:39:31,890
Master Qiaoqi.

885
00:39:32,070 --> 00:39:32,630
Master Qiaoqi.

886
00:39:32,630 --> 00:39:33,480
Wait, wait.

887
00:39:34,400 --> 00:39:35,410
Wait, wait.

888
00:39:35,430 --> 00:39:36,500
What's wrong?

889
00:39:36,530 --> 00:39:37,990
I've finished all my work.

890
00:39:38,150 --> 00:39:39,110
Master Qiaoqi.

891
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:41,510
The guests are praising your cooking.

892
00:39:41,510 --> 00:39:42,840
Show them a little more.

893
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:45,110
Don't leave all the work to me.

894
00:39:45,110 --> 00:39:46,120
Where's Chef Jia?

895
00:39:46,230 --> 00:39:47,110
He's the head chef.

896
00:39:47,110 --> 00:39:48,570
Let him grill the skewers.

897
00:39:49,030 --> 00:39:49,880
Master Qiaoqi.

898
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:51,190
Please don't make it difficult for me.

899
00:39:51,190 --> 00:39:52,590
The guest specifically asked for you.

900
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:54,590
He's the financial backer of our hotel.

901
00:39:54,590 --> 00:39:56,520
Even the boss has to treat him well.

902
00:39:57,590 --> 00:39:59,080
Financial backer?

903
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:00,840
Has he paid me overtime?

904
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:03,880
Master Qiaoqi, thank you
for your hard work.

905
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:07,760
Miyu.

906
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:24,510
Thank you.

907
00:40:33,030 --> 00:40:34,760
Why is it all champagne?

908
00:40:34,760 --> 00:40:35,840
Is there no red wine?

909
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:36,630
There's red wine over there,

910
00:40:36,630 --> 00:40:37,830
at the buffet table.

911
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:39,510
Waiter.

912
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:44,000
Hello, waiter.

913
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:48,710
I'm sorry.

914
00:40:48,710 --> 00:40:49,510
Are you okay?

915
00:40:50,070 --> 00:40:51,110
Thank you, sir.

916
00:40:51,110 --> 00:40:53,640
Otherwise, I would have
fallen to the ground.

917
00:40:54,150 --> 00:40:57,000
Your suit must be expensive.

918
00:40:57,000 --> 00:40:58,510
I'm really sorry.

919
00:40:58,630 --> 00:40:59,150
Come on.

920
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:01,020
It doesn't matter, it's fine.

921
00:41:03,140 --> 00:41:04,260
Mr. Ji,

922
00:41:04,290 --> 00:41:06,870
did you just come back from abroad?

923
00:41:08,670 --> 00:41:09,510
Do you know me?

924
00:41:09,670 --> 00:41:11,360
Everyone here knows you.

925
00:41:11,510 --> 00:41:12,840
You are Mr. Duan's friend,

926
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:14,280
Mr. Ji Feng,

927
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:16,840
the star manager of Siwei Group.

928
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:18,460
Just an acting one.

929
00:41:18,670 --> 00:41:19,840
Mr. Ji.

930
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:23,070
We are so destined to meet.

931
00:41:23,070 --> 00:41:24,960
Why don't we exchange WeChat?

932
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,450
I'll scan your code.

933
00:41:34,050 --> 00:41:35,890
[Personal Receipt code]

934
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:36,000
What do you mean?

935
00:41:36,030 --> 00:41:37,320
Adding a contact is too troublesome.

936
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:38,190
This is more direct.

937
00:41:38,190 --> 00:41:40,000
No, you misunderstood.

938
00:41:40,110 --> 00:41:42,590
I just wanted to add you
as my WeChat friend

939
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:44,550
to ask for your advice

940
00:41:44,550 --> 00:41:45,800
on some professional matters.

941
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:46,260
Sure.

942
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:48,400
Pay me the dry-cleaning fee first.

943
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:49,360
This custom suit of mine

944
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:50,920
costs 3,280 yuan to wash once.

945
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:52,320
Just give me 3,000 yuan.

946
00:41:53,110 --> 00:41:55,880
Mr. Ji, you should not let me take
all the blame for this.

947
00:41:55,880 --> 00:41:57,110
It was an accident.

948
00:41:57,110 --> 00:41:59,840
Besides, so many people are here.

949
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:00,960
It's so crowded.

950
00:42:04,670 --> 00:42:06,480
It's her. It's her.

